author: Xbox
description:
Step into the dark realms of Norse mythology in Jotunnslayer: Hordes of Hel, a gripping roguelike horde-survivor where survival is earned in blood. Battle relentless waves of enemies, wield the divine power of ancient Viking deities, and become a god-like warrior in the ultimate fight against the forces of Hel.

- Roguelike combat meets mythic mayhem

- Unlock divine blessings and powerful abilities

- Explore brutal Norse realms

- Face epic bosses and endless hordes

Do you have what it takes to survive?

Available now on Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/jotunnslayer-hordes-of-hel/9nxtls86cvtq

Cronos: The New Dawn is a brutal, time-bending survival horror where every fight could be your last. Survive the brutal wastelands of the future, fight nightmarish merging creatures and jump back in time to harvest souls as you seek to uncover the origins of the apocalypse that wiped out humanity.

Launches September 5, 2025 on Xbox Series X|S and PC.
Get the Deluxe Edition for up to 48 hours of early access starting September 3.

Buy Now and Don’t let them merge.
